登録方法です

00:38:15.662 --> 00:38:18.966 align:start position:29% line:-1
次はデバイスの個別化です

00:38:20.000 --> 00:38:25.239 align:start position:12% line:-2
DailyRoutineRelevance
Providerはコンテンツを

00:38:25.339 --> 00:38:28.976 align:start position:34% line:-2
